	data-armory-ids=&quot;100153&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Relic&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;td&gt; Fractal &lt;&#x2F;td&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tbody&gt;&lt;&#x2F;table&gt;
&lt;hr&#x2F;&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are having difficulty maintaining Alacrity uptime, replace Sigil of Bursting with Sigil of Concentration for a small DPS loss.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Food: &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;95942&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Meaty Asparagus Skewer&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enhancement: &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;48917&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Toxic Tuning Crystal&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;build&quot;&gt;Build&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;pre data-lang=&quot;chatlink&quot; class=&quot;language-chatlink z-code&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-chatlink&quot; data-lang=&quot;chatlink&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-source z-chatlink&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-definition z-string z-begin&quot;&gt;[&amp;amp;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;DQctPRg9OzsjDwAAggEAAIEBAACDAQAA7RIAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAADWQBWAGYAAA==&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-definition z-string z-end&quot;&gt;]&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;div data-armory-embed=&#x27;skills&#x27; data-armory-ids=&#x27;21750,10247,10232,10234,29519&#x27;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;&lt;div data-armory-embed=&#x27;specializations&#x27; data-armory-ids=&#x27;45,24,59&#x27; data-armory-45-traits=&#x27;670,669,1687&#x27; data-armory-24-traits=&#x27;721,1690,753&#x27; data-armory-59-traits=&#x27;2110,2174,2169&#x27;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;rotation&quot;&gt;Rotation&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Always start with:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Opener:&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10216&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Phantasmal Warlock (Staff 3)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dodge --&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;40184&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Vortex (Ambush)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10331&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Armor (Staff 4)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10169&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Storm (Staff 5)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your highest priority skill is &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;40184&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Vortex (Ambush). To use &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;40184&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Vortex (Ambush), you will either have to dodge or use a Shatter with 3 clones to gain Mirage Cloak.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skill Priority:&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dodge and use &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;40184&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Vortex without letting your energy fill up completely&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10216&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Phantasmal Warlock (Staff 3) --&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;21750&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Signet of the Ether --&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10216&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Phantasmal Warlock (Staff 3)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10331&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Armor (Staff 4)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10169&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Storm (Staff 5)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;On top of this, you want to use a Shatter skill whenever you have 3 clones.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Shatter Priority:&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10190&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Cry of Frustration&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10191&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Mind Wrack&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After using a Shatter, you will gain Mirage Cloak and automatically perform &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;40184&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Vortex (Ambush). Do not use any other skills until you have finished casting &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;40184&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Vortex (Ambush), as using any other skill will cancel &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;40184&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Vortex (Ambush).&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;crowd-control&quot;&gt;Crowd Control&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your CC skills are, in order of priority:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CC Skills:&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;29519&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Signet of Humility&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10169&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Storm (Staff 5) (Delay this skill in your rotation if you know a CC bar is coming up)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10234&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Signet of Midnight (Small CC, moderate DPS loss)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10232&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Signet of Domination (Big CC, big DPS loss)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;advanced-tips&quot;&gt;Advanced Tips&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10192&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Distortion is also a very long immune skill, scaling up to a maximum of 3 seconds with the number of clones you currently have, and should be your panic button. It can also be used to dodge mechanics on various raids to increase your damage uptime.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;video&quot;&gt;Video&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
