&lt;h2 id=&quot;rotation&quot;&gt;Rotation&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Always start with:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Opener:&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10216&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Phantasmal Warlock (Staff 3)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dodge --&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;40184&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Vortex (Ambush)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;41065&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Crystal Sands&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10331&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Armor (Staff 4)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10169&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Storm (Staff 5)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;40200&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; False Oasis&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dodge --&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;40184&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Vortex (Ambush)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pick up mirror from &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;40200&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; False Oasis --&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;40184&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Vortex (Ambush)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pick up mirror from &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;41065&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Crystal Sands using &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;45449&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Jaunt --&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;40184&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Vortex (Ambush)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your highest priority skill is &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;40184&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Vortex (Ambush). To use &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;40184&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Vortex (Ambush), you will either have to dodge or to pick up a Mirror to gain Mirage Cloak.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skill Priority:&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;41065&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Crystal Sands (pick up mirror in boss hitbox using &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;45449&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Jaunt)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;40200&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; False Oasis (pick up mirror where you casted &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;40200&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; False Oasis)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dodge and use &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;40184&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Vortex without letting your energy fill up completely&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10216&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Phantasmal Warlock (Staff 3)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10331&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Armor (Staff 4)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10169&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Storm (Staff 5)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You do not need to pick up the mirage mirror created using &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;41065&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Crystal Sands or &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;40200&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; False Oasis immediately, as they will last on the ground for 8 seconds before disappearing. This allows you to squeeze in other skills from your priority list, allowing for higher DPS.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Take care not to cancel &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;40184&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Vortex (Ambush) by casting another skill while &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;40184&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Vortex (Ambush) is casting.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;crowd-control&quot;&gt;Crowd Control&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your CC skills are, in order of priority:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CC Skills:&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10169&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chaos Storm (Staff 5) (Delay this skill in your rotation if you know a CC bar is coming up)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10287&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Diversion (more clones more CC)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10234&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Signet of Midnight (Small CC, moderate DPS loss)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10232&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Signet of Domination (Big CC, big DPS loss)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you CC&#x27;ed using &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10287&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Diversion, you want to generate more clones by casting &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10216&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Phantasmal Warlock (Staff 3) as soon as possible as much of your damage from this build comes from your clones. You can also use &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10310&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Phase Retreat (Staff 2) --&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;45449&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Jaunt to generate 2 clones and move back onto the boss as &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10310&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Phase Retreat (Staff 2) moves you away from the boss.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;advanced-tips&quot;&gt;Advanced Tips&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10192&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Distortion is also a very long immune skill, scaling up to a maximum of 3 seconds with the number of clones you currently have, and should be your panic button. It can also be used to dodge mechanics on various raids to increase your damage uptime.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
